{"tid":594873,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多on9仔以為可以係dse口試玩9其他人","createTime":"2018-03-16T07:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T08:03:27.000Z","uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbbfd782bfddb6f4bace7833c381f31235e6072","tid":594873,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"重考的選擇<br />\n<br />\n若考生的口試表現受到程序上、技術上或人為錯誤的影響，或因口試的錄影<br />\n質素不理想導致考生的表現未能得到重新評核，考生或會獲選擇重考口試的<br />\n機會，由於分數調整並不適用於口試，考評局會安排考生在另一時段重考，<br />\n而重考的分數會取代原有分數。然而，考生並非強制參與這一類重考。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詳見公開考試異常事件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/candidates/irregularities/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2Fcandidates%2Firregularities%2F&d=pKsHBioDYNz6J0QO26OaKLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=58e5a8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/candidates/irregularities/</a>"},{"pid":"abc815844a4ef0527ee4b5781180373d7dc1e8ec","tid":594873,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"玩鳩完第一批之後申請重考"},{"pid":"bdb9decbe32b7cae2c910171c6149d173196384a","tid":594873,"uid":141330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:03:27.000Z","msg":"重考嗰陣補多句：走？我睇你走得去邊！"}]}